                     <interp inst="t18461026-2034-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 7 coats and 1 pair of trowsers, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18461026-name-309" type="victimName">
